    ns1:otherInformation """This course contributes from Higher Education imprint and ulterior professional exercice to the Sustainable Development Goals (SDG) by United Nations (UN):
SDG 9: Build resilient infrastructure, promote inclusive and sustainable industrialization and foster innovation.
SDG 12: Ensure sustainable consumption and production patterns."""@es ;
    ns1:periodEndingMonth "Enero"@es ;
    ns1:periodStartingMonth "Septiembre"@es ;
