    schema:courseSchedule <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/563000071/2025-26/eventSchedule> ;
    schema:description "A topic selection on mechanical assemblies, joining processes, design and manufacturing tolerances are studied in relationship with their use in the design and development of products. The integration of manual and automated assembly processes into manufacturing systems, together with the economic and sustainability implications in product development and product life cycle are also analysed."@es ;
